settings.description: A partial recreation of 8-4 from Super Mario Bros.

You have to do the least logical thing to escape from jail, if you did the least logical thing you win and if not you will stay lost in an endless loop.
Test some of your skills with the Tanooki Suit in this brief adventure up in the sky!
Even if this editor seems kinda robust, it's kinda fun trying to build levels under the GBA's limitation. Level's mostly focused on the Triangular Block's mechanics.
After a "long" adventure, you finally made it! Now you must go through the entire world to get to the final boss, bowser. Take the Hammer suit with you and a few more powerups to defeat him!
Suppose it's time for an old washed up mario flash level maker to step foot into a new light... with a new honestly great level making program as well! hopefully this level's fun too!
This is a replica of the very first Level of "Plok!" for the SNES. Also, its a test to see how well this editor was and to be honest, is kinda frustrating, but thats expected for a project in Alpha.
Warning : This level might be buggy
